    • toString

      public String toString()
      Returns a String of the Territoy name, a list of its neighbors (bordering Territories) and value. In the form of: NORTH-WEST-TERRITORY, BORDERS:[ALASKA, ALBERTA, ONTARIO, GREENLAND] OWNER: NONE, NUMARMIES: 0 (value information dependent on what the generic anyType is)
